author: becka11y
msg: Pass objects as JSON string arguments rather than query string params.

This will allow passing more complex objects (for example Contacts) as parameters.  Modified InvokedUrlCommand to rely on JSON calls to convert passed string into dictionary.   Simplified intergerValueFromKey since numbers are converted to NSNumber. Also, add notice in index.html that json2.js is required for iOS < 4.0
